_meanings:
{@--1@} Proposing part of a
stanza to another to be completed,
the part of a stanza so given to be
completed; {#kaH SrIpatiH kA vizamA#}
{#samasyA#} <ls>Subhāṣ.</ls>; (thus the lines
{#vAgarTAviva saMpUktO, SatakowipravistaraM; tarAsAhaM#}
{#puroDAya#} are completed by {#nemuH sarve surAH#}
{#SivO#}.)

{@--2@} (Hence) Completing or
filling up what is incomplete;  
{#gOrIva patyA suBagA#} 
{#kadAcitkartrIyamapyarDatanUsamasyAM#} <ls>N. 7. 82</ls> ({#samasyA#} = {#saMGawanaM#}).
